00:00:17.280 --> 00:00:23.760
hands full of the mozzarella or your favorite
cheese. Place you hand right by the sauce

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:48.140
edge. You would sprinkle on a little estrange
there or you put to much just pick it right

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:57.269
up and put it back somewhere else. Put some
