00:00:57.269 --> 00:01:05.890
cheese pizza. Then we are going to take the
chicken. Our tongs and just place that on

00:01:05.890 --> 00:01:14.510
this is the chicken that we cooked in the
white wine reduction. A little bit of garlic,

00:01:14.510 --> 00:01:30.091
salt, and pepper nothing to fancy. It is always
good to arrange the toppings, no matter what

00:01:30.091 --> 00:01:36.160
you are putting on there, so that every slice
has some of everything. In this case, it is

00:01:36.160 --> 00:01:41.750
easy because it is just one topping. You always
want to do your toppings in layers when you

00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:49.470
are making your pizza. You should put the
first topping on all the way through the pizza

00:01:49.470 --> 00:01:52.210
